Police are investigating a case of child neglect in Katlehong after an infant was abandoned on the roadside in the area. JOHANNESBURG - Police are investigating a case of child neglect in Katlehong after an infant was abandoned on the roadside in the area. Police were alerted by community members on Thursday.The baby boy is in a stable condition and has been taken to a hospital for treatment.The police's Mega Ndobe says, The baby was found in good condition and was later taken to hospital for a check-up. We re calling on the community members to assist us find the mother of the baby. (Edited by Zamangwane Shange)